{
  "stem": "964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, over there, you can stay with him for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody told me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my younger brother was in the shul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was-- you know, all the Jewish people congregate and you comes into a new place, you go to the shul there, you find-- you find your people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to this guy, and I told him I came from Warsaw and if I could sleep over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he gave-- there was a fireplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was-- was-- was a fireplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and he said, you can lay down here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He gave me a piece of old rag, and I should sleep on this piece of rag.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it's better than sleeping in the shul, or being in the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was laying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the morning, I got up nice and quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wash myself, and dress, and got sneaked out to the door so not to disturb them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, make the story short, after three days, he said, look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot be here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have no room for you, these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I saw what-- what he-- what he means.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to the shul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there we were sleeping like sardines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no room!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sleeping or standing, or sleeping one next to the other-- I met a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was his honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He married-- the girl wouldn't go with him until he marry her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he married her a day before crossing the border, his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they came into [NON-ENGLISH] And there he is on the-- on the floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is his honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a while in [NON-ENGLISH], I found work in a bakery.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
